            <title>[QPIDJMS-198] Blocked Send on a MessageProducer waiting for credit not unblocked on remote close of the producer</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/QPIDJMS-198</link>
                <project id="12314524" key="QPIDJMS">Qpid JMS</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When a send is blocked waiting for credit and the sender link is remotely closed the send is never unblocked.  The send completion needs to be notified of the with the same failure error as is applied to in-flight sends awaiting a disposition. &lt;/p&gt;</description>
